Richard Boone https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Boone 0 Richard Allen Boone (June 18, 1917 – January 10, 1981) was an American actor who starred in over 50 films and was notable for his roles in Westerns and for the TV series Have Gun – Will Travel.
